name: Nursing Reference Center PLUS (Ebsco)
description: Master nursing best practices with the premier source for evidence-based information designed specifically for nurses. Unmatched in scope, nurses use Nursing Reference Center Plus to get answers to questions quickly, access care plans, watch video demonstrations, strengthen nursing skills, earn continuing education credits and much more. **This resource in available on trial until March 18, 2016. Please send feedback to susan.jacobs@nyu.edu **
